If you don't know how to make them add to the right equipment slot, here is how.
In the server folder, there's a file called Item.java.
To add the torso armor to the right slot, add [code]13884, 13887, 13858, 13870[/code] after [code]public static int body[] = {[/code]
To add the leggings to the right slot, add [code]13890, 13893, 13861, 13873[/code] after [code]public static int legs[] = {[/code]
To add the head objects to the right slot, add [code]13896, 13864, 13876[/code] after [code]public static int fullHelm[] = {[/code] If that doesn't make it equip to the head slot, try adding those to [code]public static int Helm[] = {[/code]
